Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Dead or alive　狭間に揺られて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}彷徨えば　Right to left to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}孤独の招待　感情の消退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:55.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}踊る1 2 3 steps on this dark stage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Raise your flag, march on, fight
