Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:08.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}溢る力が　不意に嗤い出した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:14.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}真実は何処へ　探して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Where's my soul? Where's my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}現実に呑まれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:24.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Don't hesitate, go this way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}理解らない　構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}紛い力振るっても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:34.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}ただこの世界を生き抜けよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:39.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}嗚呼　失くした哀しみがまた疼いてく…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Misery-World
